    "executiveSummary": {
      "text": "Ads-Tec Energy makes battery-buffered fast charging systems and related energy management software. The interesting part of the story is not simply EV charging demand, but whether the company can prove that its buffer technology solves grid-connection bottlenecks in locations where conventional ultra-fast chargers are hard or expensive to install. The shares still look speculative because adoption depends on project execution, channel build-out and funding discipline rather than a long record of recurring cash generation."
